item.title: Watch in Awe as This Motorized Paper Airplane Soars Through the Sky!
item.description: Watch in Awe as This Motorized Paper Airplane Soars Through the Sky! Have you ever wanted to fly a paper airplane, but wished it could go farther and faster? Well, now you can! Motorized paper airplanes are the latest craze in aviation, and they are sure to amaze you. What is a motorized paper airplane? A motorized paper airplane is a paper airplane that has been fitted with an electric motor.
